      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOLD ALASKA (4) boasts a strong record this journey with six wins and three minors from 11 tries. Hit the frame latest (25.57) when third at this track in a Grade 5. Makes strong appeal on best. OSCAR MAGIC (1) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Borneo Traveler (22.11) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Expected to be in this for a long way. WAIKARIE VENOM (3) showed good early speed and led throughout to score by a space when a 7 length winner at Rockhampton over 407m (23.46). Has a good record at this journey. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to his credit. Likely to be in the finish. GOLDSTAR HECTOR (2) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
